<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4894408>
    dc:description "FIGURES 46–63: LM and SEM micrographs of Fragilaria micra (type material). Figs 46–58. Diminution series of Fragilaria micra. Figs 59, 60. SEM external valve view. Fig. 61. SEM internal valve view. Internal foramina appear longer than external. Fig. 62. SEM external valve view. Detail of valve end showing small, indistinct opening of rimoportula. External opening simple, slightly larger than adjacent areolae. Fig. 63. SEM internal valve view. Detail of valve end showing internal opening of rimoportula. Scale bars: LM = 10 µm, SEM in Figs 59–61 = 5 µm, Figs 62, 63 = 1 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4894408/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

